Please submit Hostel fees installment form for 2016 (Jul-Nov) *along with
first installment fee receipt of Rs.10000/-* to HM Office for approval and
forward to Hostel Office.


Disclaimer: This is only applicable to existing MS and PhD Scholars. (Not
applicable to New MS and PhD Scholars)






